is a [[Japanese clans|Japanese clan]] descended from {{ill|Furutama-no-mikoto|ja|布留多摩命|draft}}. Their shrine is {{ill|Yagi Shrine|ja|夜疑神社|draft}}

They owned [[Wakasa Oniga Castle]]
[[ja:八木氏]]

