Furutama-no-mikoto (布留多摩命) is a son of [[Watatsumi]]. He is an ancestor of many clans including the {{Interlanguage link|Owari clan|lt=Owari clan|ja|尾張国造|draft}}, the {{Interlanguage link|Yamato no Kuni no Miyatsuko|lt=Yamato clan|simple|draft}}, the [[Kamo clan]], the {{ill|Kubiki Kokuzo|ja|久比岐国造|draft|complete=true}}, the {{ill|Akashi no Kuni no Miyatsuku|lt=Akashi Kokuzo|ja|明石国造|draft|complete=true}} and the {{ill|Yagi clan|ja|八木氏|draft|complete=true}} of which he is also the [[Ujigami]] worshipped at {{ill|Yagi Shrine|ja|夜疑神社|draft}}.

He had several children including {{ill|Takeuioki no mikoto|ja|武位起命|draft}}'''|, {{ill|Amanosakitama no mikoto|ja|天前玉命|draft|lt1=Amanosakitama no mikoto|lt2=尾張国造}}|, {{ill|Kuroshima Isone hime|ja|黒島磯根御気姫命|draft}}''', '''{{ill|Onotehime|lt=Ohonutehime|ja|大野手比売|draft|lt2=大鐸比売命}}'''

